description: The prosecutor’s office at the International Criminal Court (ICC) has demanded an end to the intimidation of its staff, saying such threats could constitute an offence against the “administration of justice” by the world’s permanent war crimes court.
title: ICC demands Israel, US end threats against the court over Gaza war probe

description: TEHRAN - Iranian Foreign Ministry spokesman on Thursday condemned US authorities for violently cracking down on students protesting against the Israeli relentless war on the Gaza Strip, saying the “mask of hypocrisy” has been removed “from the faces of the false defenders of freedom of speech and human rights”.
title: Iran says student crackdown removes ‘mask of hypocrisy’ from US face

description: The World Health Organization (WHO) has warned an Israeli incursion into Rafah would put the lives of hundreds of thousands of Palestinians at risk and turn into a “bloodbath” with the health system in shambles, Al Jazeera reported on Friday.
title: WHO warns Israeli incursion into Rafah would be a ‘bloodbath’

description: Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdogan said on Friday this his government’s move to halt trade with Israel is aimed at achieving a ceasefire in Gaza.
title: Erdogan says halting trade with Israel intended to ‘force’ Gaza ceasefire: Erdogan
